Talon, would what Wildmare is doing have an effect on Shredder?

::Shredder::

Shredder walks out of the forest, looking around. He still hadn't found a 
base, and he was getting bored. He looks down into a valley, his eyes 
narrowing when he sees the bot standing on it.

Taking out both chain guns, Shredder walks down toward the bot.

"Hey," he yells to the bot, "You a pred or maxi?"
